vote.title: Authorize a five-year cooperative purchasing agreement for the purchase, installation, hardware monitoring, and support for a secondary backup circuits for the Department of Information and Technology Services with 22nd Century Technologies, Inc. through the Sourcewell cooperative agreement - Not to exceed $12,583,720.40 - Financing: Data Services Fund (subject to annual appropriations)
